  "title": "Enco International Limited",
  "categories": ["Branding", "Motion", "Interaction"],
  "description": "ENCO Group Studio is a creative representative agency based in Seoul, South Korea. The rebrand repositioned the studio as ENCO INTERNATIONAL LIMITED, shifting its perception from a local agency to a global platform. The primary challenge was building a system that could scale internationally while remaining cohesive across diverse markets and contexts.\n\nTo address this, I developed a flexible identity system anchored by a dynamic color framework designed for visibility across cultural and geographic environments. Multiple logo lockups were created to adapt to varying formats and use cases, ensuring consistency without rigidity. A structured typographic system reinforces clarity, while motion was introduced as a key component to capture attention and communicate energy across digital platforms.\n\nThe result is a scalable identity that supports ENCO\u2019s expansion while maintaining a strong and unified presence.",
